videos.description: Kansas State guard Barry Brown splits the Kansas defense, and loses his shoe while scoring on the drive.
videos.headline: Brown loses shoe on Kansas State layup

videos.description: Kansas State's Xavier Sneed goes for a breakaway dunk, but Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk comes from out of nowhere to block Sneed from behind.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk has LeBron-like chase-down block

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike moves through the lane and catches the lob above the rim for the powerful slam.
videos.headline: Azubuike slams Graham's lob on Kansas connection

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk spots up from the corner and drills his third 3-pointer halting a Kansas State run.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk hits 3rd triple from corner for Kansas

videos.description: Makol Mawien erases Devonte' Graham's layup, and Dean Wade cleans up with a layup on the other end to cut Kansas' lead to single digits.
videos.headline: Kansas State lingering with block and layup

videos.description: Malik Newman drives to the hoop and scores through contact to extend the Jayhawks' second-half lead.
videos.headline: Newman extends Kansas' lead with and-1

videos.description: Barry Brown misses the triple, but Xavier Sneed crashes the offensive glass and gets the putback with one hand.
videos.headline: Sneed crashes boards for aggressive Kansas State putback
